---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Software engineer navigating the chaos"
	pubDate={new Date('December 22 2025')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hi! I'm a software engineer passionate about creating elegant solutions from chaotic problems.
		With experience since 2017, I've worked primarily with .NET, but I also enjoy exploring
		modern web technologies like Angular, React, and Blazor.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is my space to share thoughts, experiences, and discoveries from the ever-evolving
		world of software engineering. Expect posts about clean code, architecture patterns,
		web development, and the occasional deep dive into interesting technical challenges.
	</p>

	<p>
		When I'm not coding, you'll find me experimenting with new technologies, contributing to
		open-source projects, or writing about the lessons learned from both successes and failures
		in software development.
	</p>

	<p>
		Feel free to reach out if you'd like to discuss tech, collaborate on projects, or just
		chat about the beautiful chaos that is software engineering!
	</p>
</Layout>
